{"timestamp": "2026-04-14T14:14:41.956818Z", "level": "INFO", "logger": "resume_parser", "message": "EDUCATION\n---------\n\nBrilliant Institute of Engineering  Technology Telangana, India\nBachelor of Technology in Computer Science (AIML)  GPA: 7.010.0 June 2021  August 2025\nSaketha Junior College [Intermediate] Hyderabad, India\nMathematics, Physics and Chemistry GPA: 7.4 10.0 June 2019  August 2021\n\nLANGUAGES\n---------\n\n: Java, JavaScript, SQL\nFrontend: HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, React.js\nBackend: Java, Spring Boot, REST APIs\nDatabase: MySQL, JDBC\nTools: Git, EclipseIntelliJ\nOthers: OOPs, Agile basics\n\nEXPERIENCE\n----------\n\nJAVA FULLSTACK\n\nCERTIFICATIONS\n--------------\n\nPROGRAM Sep 01 - Dec 05\nLearned and applied Java and Spring Boot to develop backend services. Built user-friendly interfaces using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and React.js. Assisted in creating and testing REST APIs for web application features. Worked with MySQL for database design and data handling. Gained hands-on\n\nEXPERIENCE\n----------\n\nwith Git, Postman, and basic DevOps tools in a real-world developmentenvironment.\n\nPROJECTS\n--------\n\n: Digital-Wallet\nTech Stack: React, React Router, Axios, JavaScript (ES6), Spring Boot, Spring Security, Spring Data JPA, RESTful APIs, JWT, MySQL, Docker, Swagger, Lombok, Git  GitHub\nBuilt a full-stack digital wallet application enabling fund transfers, wallet top-ups, and transaction history with secure user\n\nEXPERIENCE\n----------\n\n. Developed Spring Boot REST APIs using layered architecture (Controller-Service-Repository) to handle wallet, ledger, and authentication workflows. Implemented JWT-based authentication with Role-based Authorization (USER, ADMIN) and secure Axios interceptors on frontend. Designed React UI with reusable components, React Router navigation, and protected routes for authenticated screens. Integrated Axios for API calls with token refresh flow and global state management using ContextReduxZustand. Ensured transactional consistency using @Transactional and DB row-level locking to avoid race conditions on wallet balance. Built a double-entry ledger module ensuring financial accuracy  every transaction produces both debit and credit entries. Added Admin panel to manage users (freezereactivate wallets) and monitor suspicious transactions. Designed and optimized MySQL database schema with indexed tables for scalable query performance. Applied form validation using Hibernate Validator (backend) and client-side validation in React for secure inputs. Containerized application using Docker, enabling easy deployment of backend  database environment.\n\nCERTIFICATIONS\n--------------\n\nJAVA FULLSTACK\n\nCERTIFICATIONS\n--------------\n\n: Successful Completion on JavaFullstack\n\nCERTIFICATIONS\n--------------\n\nProgram by EduBridge(Capgemini). AI Tool Workshop\nOn Successful completion of AI tools and ChatGPT workshop Conducted by be10x. SOFTSKILLS\nLearning new Technologies\nTime Management\nTeam Work\nProblem Solving", "request_id": "857d0d16-5fd9-4643-9663-04e2233d8cab"}
