{"timestamp": "2026-04-14T14:16:57.299387Z", "level": "INFO", "logger": "resume_parser", "message": "SUMMARY\n-------\n\nHR professional with solid\n\nEXPERIENCE\n----------\n\nin sourcing, recruitment, and onboarding processes. Skilled in using\nLinkedIn Recruiter, Naukri, Indeed, and ATS (TalentPathway) for managing end-to-end hiring operations. Currently enhancing knowledge in payroll and HR operations to contribute to dynamic HR teams and grow\nprofessionally within fast-paced organizations.\n\nSKILLS\n------\n\nHuman Resources  Hiring Strategies\nATS Management\nTalent Aquisition\nOnboarding Coordination\nHR Administration\nMS office\nEnd-to-End Recruitment\n\nEXPERIENCE\n----------\n\nTalent Acquisition Associate 022025  present\nW3Global Inc. Hyderabad, India\nSourced and managed 20 active candidate pipelines per month for IT and non-IT\nroles, delivering qualified talent under tight timelines. Conducted screening interviews focusing on skill fit, company culture alignment, and job motivation. Handled end-to-end recruitment cycle, including job postings, proactive\nsourcing, pre-screening, scheduling, and offer negotiations. Maintained clean and accurate records in TalentPathway ATS, supporting\ntransparent hiring processes. Partnered with hiring managers to align on role expectations, speeding up\nclosures by 20. Assisted with onboarding documentation, induction support, and facilitated\nsmooth joining formalities. Currently gaining exposure in payroll processes, HRMIS handling, and employee\nlifecycle coordination. Human Resources Intern 112024  012025\nShawave Technologies Hyderabad, India\nAssisted in sourcing and screening candidates for different roles. Coordinated interview schedules and maintained communication with applicants. Managed candidate records and supported documentation for onboarding. Provided general HR support during recruitment and onboarding processes. HR Internship Trainee 062023  072023\nImmensphere IT Solutions Bangalore, India\n\nPROJECTS\n--------\n\n: A Study On Shortlisting and Recruitment\nScreened and shortlisted resumes, ensuring alignment with role requirements and\norganizational needs. Collaborated with team members to onboard participants, ensuring a seamless\nrecruitment process. Developed comprehensive feedback reports for management, offering actionable\ninsights for process optimization.\n\nEDUCATION\n---------\n\nBachelor of Business Administration-BBA 2021  2024\nGitam University Hyderabad, India\n\nCERTIFICATIONS\n--------------\n\nRecruiting, Hiring, and\n\nPROJECTS\n--------\n\nInitiation: Starting a Talent Aquisition by hrci\nOnboarding Employees- Successful\n\nPROJECTS\n--------\n\n-Google\nUniversity of Minnesota\nNaukri Maestro Recruiter\nCredential ID: NMRP-0425-\n115427\nBEHAVIORAL\n\nSKILLS\n------\n\nProblem solving  Leadership\nTeamwork\nIntegrity\nTeam Collaboration\nCritical thinking", "request_id": "4f466e0b-18db-4bbc-9d06-f64283e4911d"}
